title: [Gyldemar Green, Forest]
description: A large maoral tree lies toppled on the ground to the west, displaying its massive root system.  Thick pieces of dried bark have separated from the trunk of the tree and provide shelter to a family of squirrels.  A break in the canopy overhead allows sunlight to filter into the area.
